                "invention-title": [
                    "Spinel type lithium titanate electrochromic film and preparation method thereof",
                    "一种尖晶石型钛酸锂电致变色薄膜及其制备方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to a spinel type lithium titanate electrochromic film and a preparation method thereof, and belongs to the field of preparation of electrochromic devices. The preparation method comprises the following steps that Ti {OCH (CH3) 2} 4, lithium hydroxide and hydrogen peroxide are dissolved according to a certain proportion and react to prepare an LTO precursor solution, the LTO precursor solution is prepared into a film on conductive glass serving as a substrate in a blade coating mode, and then the LTO electrochromic film is obtained after low-temperature heat treatment is conducted for a period of time. The crystal structure of the spinel-type lithium titanate electrochromic film prepared by the method is a single-phase spinel structure, and the spinel-type lithium titanate electrochromic film has excellent optical modulation capability; the preparation method disclosed by the invention is suitable for low-temperature synthesis, has the advantages of low energy consumption, no pollution and good repeatability, and can be suitable for large-scale production."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及一种尖晶石型钛酸锂电致变色薄膜及其制备方法，属于电致变色器件制备领域。本发明所述制备方法包括如下步骤：将Ti{OCH(CH3)2}4、氢氧化锂及双氧水按一定比例溶解，反应配置得到LTO前驱体溶液，结合刮涂的方式将LTO前驱液在衬底为导电玻璃上制成薄膜，然后经过一段时间低温热处理得到LTO电致变色薄膜。本发明制备得到的尖晶石型钛酸锂电致变色薄膜的晶体结构为单相尖晶石结构，具有优秀的光学调制能力；本发明的制备方法适用于低温合成，具有低能耗、无污染和重复性好的优点，可适用于大规模的生产。"
                }
            ]
